snippet.title: MegaMan X: Corrupted - X Intro Stage
snippet.description:
Happy New Year everyone!


It's been a very good year for MMXC and we have done a lot of progress including moving away from Flash.

I hope you like this video, it took us lot of time and effort to make this stage.

Thank you for your support!


** Disclaimer **
This is a Fan Game and not affiliated with Capcom.

Megaman X and all other megaman material are owned by Capcom.
